can you explain me about the planets data

The planets data can be found in the image "test_2.png" and in the table "planet_2.csv". Jupiter is the largest planet in our solar system, and it's visible as the biggest sphere in the image.

The population density data can be observed in the image "pie_1.png", where you can see people, stalls, and visible products. You can compare this with the population density data in the table "population_3.csv".
